## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b6a00-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>构造函数<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A>初始化属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b6a00-115">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b6a00-116">标识符在给定语法中必须是唯一的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b6a00-116">The identifier must be unique within a given grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b6a00-117">构造函数<xref:System.FormatException>在下列情况下引发: <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b6a00-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
